    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Exertional\ndyspnea\n, orthopnea, PND\nPeripheral edema\nFatigue\n, +/-\nsyncope\n,\nangina\nfrom poor cardiac output\n+/-\nArrhythmias\n,\nAV block\nQuiet precordium\nCrackles\nJVD\n+/-\nmurmur\nfrom mitral/tricuspid regurgitation",
