    "Management": {
      "text": "Symptom-directed\nDiuretics\nfor edema or pulmonary vascular congestion\nCaution as cardiac output preload dependant\nCaution with afterload reduction as may cause profound\nhypotension\nTreat\narrhythmias\nAvoid\ndigoxin\nin amyloidosis as sensitivity to dig-induced arrhythmias common",
